To get the status for a node:
If the node is nil, clear the status' string; exit.
Put the node's selected nodette count into a count.
If the count is 0, format the node's nodettes' count and "cosa" or "cosas" into the status' string.
If the count is not 0, format the count and "cosa seleccionada" or "cosas seleccionadas" into the status' string.
If the node is root-level, exit.
If the node's path is read-only, append " (s)" to the status' string.

To handle copy given a node:
If the node is root-level, cluck; exit.
If nothing is selected in the node, show error "No estoy seguro de lo que quieres que copie."; exit.
Show status "Copiando...".
Destroy the finder's clipboard in the file system.
Create the finder's clipboard in the file system.
Copy any selected nodettes in the node returning a count.
Show the desktop.
Show status the count and "ítem copiado" or "ítems copiados".
Flush the event queue.

